name: Undead Unleashed (Innistrad: Midnight Hunt Commander 2021 Precon Decklist)

main.name: Wilhelt, the Rotcleaver
main.oracle_text:
Whenever another Zombie you control dies, if it didn't have decayed, create a 2/2 black Zombie creature token with decayed. (It can't block. When it attacks, sacrifice it at end of combat.)
At the beginning of your end step, you may sacrifice a Zombie. If you do, draw a card.

card.name: Curse of the Restless Dead
card.oracle_text:
Enchant player
Whenever a land enchanted player controls enters, you create a 2/2 black Zombie creature token with decayed. (It can't block. When it attacks, sacrifice it at end of combat.)

card.name: Ravenous Rotbelly
card.oracle_text: When Ravenous Rotbelly enters, you may sacrifice up to three Zombies. When you sacrifice one or more Zombies this way, each opponent sacrifices that many creatures.
card.flavor_text: The patrol found the graf empty save for a few well-chewed bones.

card.name: Empty the Laboratory
card.oracle_text: Sacrifice X Zombies, then reveal cards from the top of your library until you reveal a number of Zombie creature cards equal to the number of Zombies sacrificed this way. Put those cards onto the battlefield and the rest on the bottom of your library in a random order.

card.name: Curse of Unbinding
card.oracle_text:
Enchant player
At the beginning of enchanted player's upkeep, that player reveals cards from the top of their library until they reveal a creature card. Put that card onto the battlefield under your control. That player puts the rest of the revealed cards into their graveyard.

card.name: Prowling Geistcatcher
card.oracle_text:
Whenever you sacrifice another creature, exile it. If that creature was a token, put a +1/+1 counter on Prowling Geistcatcher.
When Prowling Geistcatcher leaves the battlefield, return each card exiled with it to the battlefield under your control.

card.oracle_text: {3}, {T}, Sacrifice another Zombie: Create two tokens that are copies of the sacrificed creature.
card.flavor_text: Furious and unable to separate, the bitter rivals consoled themselves by splitting everything else they saw in half.

card.name: Drown in Dreams

• Target player draws X cards.
